<subSubSection id="A5743DD502DE9C4A6E793B0E3AADD1AC" pageId="null" pageNumber="351" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="1B2D0A11C7B29B1EA89A39D14D5E7D7E" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Violetter Schwingel</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="15F7291F7F02E633866ADD39A4145355" pageId="null" pageNumber="351" type="description">
<paragraph id="E63D5E92B5441DC76397518918186667" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="75F0CA3B50A5E45C618591F0752B0A16" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Festuca" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="351" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="heterophylla">
<emphasis id="186BB448528DCCAA808F102E24AAF686" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">F. heterophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 12) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="A07C57247F5C3EDB1B02C3018DB8D339" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">15-40 cm hoch</emphasis>
, horstbildend, die 
<emphasis id="FF9E60C5824FCC83096F0D2DE60F6436" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">
Triebe jedoch meist extravaginal; 
<normalizedToken id="646AB75028CB270D5F08A51A4849D692" originalValue="borstenförmige" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">borstenfoermige</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="A9CDE71DBD8BF088FC2AE344E5BBB16E" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
der nicht 
<normalizedToken id="EB90829C6166EB022C4AA4111347C0B4" originalValue="blühenden" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">bluehenden</normalizedToken>
Triebe im Querschnitt 5eckig, mit 5-9 Nerven und 7-9 
<normalizedToken id="4031A6A17CA99EF523D537B8C1B1E732" originalValue="Strängen" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Straengen</normalizedToken>
von Festigungsgewebe; 
<normalizedToken id="EB21C81209446D6179DAB14FAB5825DC" originalValue="Ährchen" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Aehrchen</normalizedToken>
meist violett 
<normalizedToken id="D5EEE9FE83392696A86F443622724E47" originalValue="überlaufen" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">ueberlaufen</normalizedToken>
.
</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="C1E55D9CC210AAD936314563F415C6B0" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer bis Herbst.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6F2C37BBDB49CE556A62D45745BC7E29" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">
<emphasis id="E973B99672FFB60F546725B2AC12AFB1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="45A805218D4727CC7EBCE7BEFB225B4E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">14:</emphasis>
Material aus botanischen 
<normalizedToken id="5F5A974207E7D318DCA13F5279446C81" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
(
<normalizedToken id="8FB62C8161846DE4610F69EE2F6F5D9F" originalValue="Stählin" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Staehlin</normalizedToken>
1929).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="EB3FE72958629B6F34B628040AAEC7E1" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">
<emphasis id="4EBAC7E53840F867B016B0AD63EBB842" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Standort.</emphasis>
Alpin und subalpin. Neutrale bis schwach saure, feinerdereiche 
<normalizedToken id="66EBCC5464085375160216554C67D179" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Boeden</normalizedToken>
. Weiden, Trockenrasen, Wildheuplanken.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="EA12511CC54C0DA88A00B21BAE643BA1" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">
<emphasis id="6D55A77350C0DA71E57361E4EAFB2262" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">
Verbreitung. Mittel- und 
<normalizedToken id="9B772833BC459B1FDD76236B1F180AB3" originalValue="südeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">suedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Gebirgspflanze:
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="159670E2D81EDE1462C8DCC7A3139976" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
, Alpen, 
<normalizedToken id="F1CBE14EBA619E184451F136A9697C95" originalValue="Südjura" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Suedjura</normalizedToken>
, Karpaten, Gebirge der Balkanhalbinsel, Kaukasus (?), Iran (?). - Im Gebiet: Alpen, 
<normalizedToken id="9EDCE29810DA3A89E3FD97191A7C0862" originalValue="Südjura" pageId="null" pageNumber="351">Suedjura</normalizedToken>
, Solothurner Jura (Hasenmatt).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
